{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I did it for-- for a while, for a few days, then he took me off and he gave me a job in the washroom.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a big washroom, big enough for 1,000 people to wash in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my job together with other prisoners was to clean that washroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That job did not give any privileges to these prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was no privilege like to escape a transport or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were just like anybody else, but we had to wash the washroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The reason he gave it to me is because I had a red band, and as I work in the washroom, I got a white band, which said the washroom [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he told me not to be too visible in the courtyard, so I should put the white band on top of the red band.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was a little wider.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, the [? flitzers ?] had to be, the head had to be shaved like every 10 days or two weeks, whatever, very short periods so they should always keep a very bald head, so they should be visible.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He told me if-- to try to avoid when the barber comes, I should hide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did, and I had little hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then three weeks later-- what I want to mention also-- is that at that time, you know, the Allies were starting to come closer to the invasion.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot of bombing and-- all over Western Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Allied bombers also bombed Mechelen because Mechelen was a-- an important railroad center.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were railroad-- huge railroad yards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were bombing these railroad yards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many of the bombs did not explode.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them were-- maybe they were defective.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
